name: Ut per litteras apostolicas
description: LITPA represents an electronic version of the renowned Registres et lettres des Papes du XIIIe siècle (32 vols.; Rome, 1883- ) and the Registres et lettres des Papes du XIVe siècle (48 vols.; Rome, 1899- ). In addition, it contains a large amount of unpublished material.
